b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Koala AI and Surfer share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Seo Tools, Multilingual, Api Access. Where Koala AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Templates and Tone Control, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Surfer uniquely offers Team Collaboration and Browser Extension, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Koala AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Surfer scores 8/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Koala AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $9/mo, compared to Surfer's starting price of $89/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
